data.description:
Discover the serene life in Simms, TX with this 3-bedroom, 2-bath remodeled home, nestled on a scenic 10-acre parcel teeming with native trees. Enjoy the privilege of a stocked pond surrounded by fenced acreage, complete with 2 work sheds one with electricity.   With Texarkana and Dekalb only minutes away, every convenience is within reach.  The home showcases fresh paint, modernized bathrooms, and an updated kitchen boasting newer appliances. The stained and stamped concrete flooring adds rustic charm. The robust metal frame and durable hardy board concrete siding promise low maintenance. In the rear, find a handy carport.  

Revel in the perfect blend of privacy and open space.
